hits.name: Altearah Bio Concentrate Gift Set - Pack of 5 5x14ml
hits.excerpt: A set of 5 concentrates. Royal purple, orange, turquoise, emerald and white concentrates.
hits.description:
Altearah Bio brings to you a wide range of aromatherapy products to mesmerize your senses. These products are created using Chromotherapy, a method of treatment based on the use of colours. The range features 14 colours, each blended with organic essential oils and specific benefits for your wellbeing. The colours are designed to match and stabilize your mood to offer you instant wellness. Rooted in nature, they are sure to leave you with a deep and unforgettable experience.


About the Product:
A complete package to revive your body and mind, this set of five concentrates from Altearah Bio makes a perfect gifting idea. It consists of five concentrates in five colours, each symbolizing specific emotions and benefits to uplift your mood.

Features:
Royal Purple is the colour of life and strength
Orange is the colour of mother, creativity, inner strength and sensuality. It enhances your inner strength by offering you peace
Emerald symbolizes breathing, space, welcoming, openness and confidence
Turquoise sf the colour of communication, clarity, sharing, tranquility and beauty.
White is colour of purity, transparency, clarification

How to Use:
Put a few drops on your wrists, rub to smooth in the Concentrate and then
breathe in.
Apply them to specific areas to resolve deep problems.

Ingredients:
Royal Purple: Cedar, Lavandin, Patchouli, Clove, Sweet Orange, Bergamot, Geranium, Rosemary, Juniper
Orange: Essential Oils, Sweet Orange, Lemon, Atlantic Cedar, Mandarin, Lavandin, Fragrances (Essential Oils)
Emerald: Essential Oils, Lemon, Lavandin, Sweet Orange, Bergamot, Clove, Rosemary, Mandarine, Eucalyptus, Fragrances (Essential Oils)
Turquoise: Essential Oils, Sweet Orange, Cedar, Bergamot, Eucalyptus, Lavandin, Palmarosa, Lavender, Mint, Lemon, Geranium, Fragrances (Essential Oils)
White: Tea Tree, Cedar, Lavender, Sweet Orange

hits.description:
Optimum Nutrition (ON) was founded in 1986 with a mission to set higher standards for the sports nutrition industry. As one of the few manufacturers to own and operate state-of-the-art production facilities that are GMP compliant, ON’s commitment to quality is uncompromising. You’ll appreciate the extra effort the industry leader puts into assuring ingredient purity, effortless mixing and exceptional taste.

About the Product:
Highly researched, creatine monohydrate has been shown to support muscle strength, power, and size when combined with high-intensity activities. Our Micronized Creatine Powder is made with Creapure, a creatine monohydrate known for its exceptional purity. It's also micronized (to make the particles smaller), so our powder mixes easier and stays suspended in liquid longer than non-micronized creatine supplements.

Features:
One standard teaspoon provides a full 5-gram daily maintenance dose of Creapure Creatine Monohydrate
ON’s Micronized Creatine Monohydrate is available in sizes ranging from 150 to 2,000 Grams. There’s one to fit your needs and budget

Creatine Monohydrate
